  "action_id": "1236",
  "action_title": "Sow tree seeds after wildfire",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nThree studies (including one replicated, randomized, controlled study) in the USA\u00a0examined the effect of sowing herbaceous plant seeds in burnt forest areas. One found it decreased the number and cover of native species and one found it decreased the density of tree seedlings. All three found no effect of seeding on total plant cover or species richness."
}

